# Template & Field Rules

- Templates belong to a workspace
- Each template has fields (name, label, type, required, default_value, etc)
- Field types supported: text, rich_text, select, multi_select, image, date, number, boolean
- Templates can be reused when creating pages
- Pages store field values in a `data` JSONB column

